# OpenCode Project Bootstrap for AI-Driven Development

This script creates a complete OpenCode project framework for building complex applications using specialized AI agents, skills, documentation, and project memory.

Features include:

* 13 specialized AI agents for discovery, planning, architecture, development, security, testing, documentation, and project history
* Structured project documentation and decision tracking
* Discovery-driven design process that challenges assumptions before coding begins
* MVP scope management to prevent feature creep
* Architecture and framework decision workflows
* Historical tracking of successes, failures, lessons learned, and "do not repeat" mistakes
* Documentation automation and project knowledge management
* OpenCode skills for common development workflows
* Ready-to-use prompts for project discovery and technology selection

Designed for long-term software projects where maintainability, consistency, documentation, and AI-assisted development are priorities.
